SQL.SQLRaw: SELECT Commandes.PartManuelle, Commandes.Modele, Commandes.Devis, Commandes.Mois, Commandes.TotalCommandes, Commandes.TauxAnomalie, Commandes.TotalHT, Ticket.NombreDeTicket, Ticket.NombredHeuresEstime, Biotracker.CR,Biotracker.RR,Biotracker.DR, BiotrackerN.CR CRN,BiotrackerN.RR RRN,BiotrackerN.DR DRN, CommandesN.TotalCommandes TotalCommandesN, CommandesN.TotalHT TotalHTN, TicketN.NombreDeTicket NombreDeTicketN, Commandes.Transport Transport, Commandes.TransportKit TransportKit, CommandesN.Transport TransportN, CommandesN.TransportKit TransportKitN, Kits.Qte, KitsN.Qte QteN, Facture.TotalFact, FactureN.TotalFact TotalFactN FROM (SELECT ROUND(100*(count(IF(llx_c_input_reason.label = 'Edition manuelle',llx_commande.fk_input_reason,NULL))/count(llx_c_input_reason.label)),2) AS PartManuelle, ROUND(100*(count(IF(llx_c_input_reason.label = 'Modèle de commande',llx_commande.fk_input_reason,NULL))/count(llx_c_input_reason.label)),2) AS Modele, ROUND(100*(count(IF(llx_c_input_reason.label = 'Devis',llx_commande.fk_input_reason,NULL))/count(llx_c_input_reason.label)),2) AS Devis, monthname(llx_commande.date_creation) Mois, count(llx_commande.ref) TotalCommandes, ROUND(100*(COUNT(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.control = 'Conforme après correction',llx_commande.ref,NULL))/(COUNT(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.control = 'Conforme après correction',llx_commande.ref,NULL)) + COUNT(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.control = 'Conforme',llx_commande.ref,NULL)))),2) AS TauxAnomalie, sum(llx_commande.total_ht) TotalHT, count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.cmd_type_tpt NOT LIKE 'materiel', llx_commande_extrafields.demandetpt,NULL)) Transport, count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.cmd_type_tpt = 'materiel', llx_commande_extrafields.demandetpt,NULL)) TransportKit FROM llx_commande LEFT JOIN llx_c_input_reason ON llx_commande.fk_input_reason = llx_c_input_reason.rowid LEFT JOIN llx_commande_extrafields ON llx_commande.rowid = llx_commande_extrafields.fk_object WHERE llx_commande.ref NOT LIKE 'BC-CEL%' AND llx_commande.fk_statut > 1 AND YEAR(llx_commande.date_creation) = YEAR(now()) GROUP BY month(llx_commande.date_creation)) AS Commandes LEFT JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_ticketsup.datec) Mois, Count(llx_ticketsup.ref) NombreDeTicket, SUM(llx_ticketsup_extrafields.heure_est) NombredHeuresEstime FROM llx_ticketsup LEFt JOIN llx_ticketsup_extrafields ON llx_ticketsup_extrafields.fk_object = llx_ticketsup.rowid WHERE llx_ticketsup.category_code IN("CMD","INTERNE","EQUIPEMENT") AND YEAR(llx_ticketsup.datec) = YEAR(now()) GROUP BY Month(llx_ticketsup.datec)) AS Ticket ON Ticket.Mois = Commandes.Mois LEFT JOIN (SELECT count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker LIKE 'CR%',llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker ,NULL)) AS CR, count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker LIKE 'RR%',llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker ,NULL)) AS RR,count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker LIKE 'DR%',llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker ,NULL)) AS DR, monthname(llx_commande.date_creation) Mois FROM llx_commande, llx_commande_extrafields WHERE llx_commande.rowid = llx_commande_extrafields.fk_object AND llx_commande.ref NOT LIKE 'BC-CEL%' AND YEAR(llx_commande.date_creation) = YEAR(now()) GROUP BY month(llx_commande.date_creation)) AS Biotracker ON Biotracker.Mois = Commandes.Mois LEFT JOIN (SELECT count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker LIKE 'CR%',llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker ,NULL)) AS CR, count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker LIKE 'RR%',llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker ,NULL)) AS RR,count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker LIKE 'DR%',llx_commande_extrafields.refbiotracker ,NULL)) AS DR, monthname(llx_commande.date_creation) Mois FROM llx_commande, llx_commande_extrafields WHERE llx_commande.rowid = llx_commande_extrafields.fk_object AND llx_commande.ref NOT LIKE 'BC-CEL%' AND YEAR(llx_commande.date_creation) = YEAR(now())-1 GROUP BY month(llx_commande.date_creation)) AS BiotrackerN ON BiotrackerN.Mois = Commandes.Mois LEFT JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_commande.date_creation) Mois, count(llx_commande.ref) TotalCommandes, sum(llx_commande.total_ht) TotalHT, count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.cmd_type_tpt NOT LIKE 'materiel', llx_commande_extrafields.demandetpt,NULL)) Transport, count(IF(llx_commande_extrafields.cmd_type_tpt = 'materiel', llx_commande_extrafields.demandetpt,NULL)) TransportKit FROM llx_commande LEFT JOIN llx_c_input_reason ON llx_commande.fk_input_reason = llx_c_input_reason.rowid LEFT JOIN llx_commande_extrafields ON llx_commande.rowid = llx_commande_extrafields.fk_object WHERE llx_commande.ref NOT LIKE 'BC-CEL%' AND llx_commande.fk_statut > 1 AND YEAR(llx_commande.date_creation) = YEAR(now())-1 GROUP BY month(llx_commande.date_creation)) AS CommandesN ON Commandes.Mois = CommandesN.Mois LEFT JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_ticketsup.datec) Mois, Count(llx_ticketsup.ref) NombreDeTicket, SUM(llx_ticketsup_extrafields.heure_est) NombredHeuresEstime FROM llx_ticketsup LEFt JOIN llx_ticketsup_extrafields ON llx_ticketsup_extrafields.fk_object = llx_ticketsup.rowid WHERE llx_ticketsup.category_code IN("CMD","INTERNE","EQUIPEMENT") AND YEAR(llx_ticketsup.datec) = YEAR(now())-1 GROUP BY Month(llx_ticketsup.datec)) AS TicketN ON TicketN.Mois = Commandes.Mois LEFt JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_commande.date_creation) Mois, sum(llx_commande_extrafields.quantite_a_produire) Qte FROM llx_commande LEFT JOIN llx_commande_extrafields ON llx_commande.rowid = llx_commande_extrafields.fk_object WHERE llx_commande.fk_statut > 1 AND YEAR(llx_commande.date_creation) = YEAR(now()) GROUP BY month(llx_commande.date_creation)) AS Kits ON Kits.Mois = Commandes.Mois LEFt JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_commande.date_creation) Mois, sum(llx_commande_extrafields.quantite_a_produire) Qte FROM llx_commande LEFT JOIN llx_commande_extrafields ON llx_commande.rowid = llx_commande_extrafields.fk_object WHERE llx_commande.fk_statut > 1 AND YEAR(llx_commande.date_creation) = YEAR(now())-1 GROUP BY month(llx_commande.date_creation)) AS KitsN ON KitsN.Mois = Commandes.Mois LEFT JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_facture.datef) Mois, sum(llx_facture.total) TotalFact FROM llx_facture WHERE YEAR(llx_facture.datef) = YEAR(now()) AND llx_facture.fk_statut IN (1,2) GROUP BY month(llx_facture.datef)) As Facture On Commandes.Mois = Facture.Mois LEFT JOIN (SELECT monthname(llx_facture.datef) Mois, sum(llx_facture.total) TotalFact FROM llx_facture WHERE YEAR(llx_facture.datef) = YEAR(now())-1 AND llx_facture.fk_statut IN (1,2) GROUP BY month(llx_facture.datef)) As FactureN On Commandes.Mois = FactureN.Mois
